'''Budh Planitia''' is a large basin on [[Mercury (planet)|Mercury]] located at 22.0° N, 150.9° W. It lies to the east of [[Odin Planitia]]. It falls within the [[Tolstoj quadrangle]]. It is named after the Hindu word for Mercury, [[Budha]].
