'''El''' is a [[impact crater|crater]] on [[Ganymede (moon)|Ganymede]]. It has a small "pit" in its center. Craters with such a "central pit" are common across Ganymede and are especially intriguing since they may reveal secrets about the structure of the satellite's shallow subsurface.<ref>[http://ciclops.org/view.php?id=4052&js=1 Khensu Crater on Ganymede<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>

